Instructions for obtaining a token using Bot Fazer
1. Register or log in
Go to the BotFazer website and either register a new account or log in if you already have one.
2. Create a new bot
Click on the "Create a bot" button.
Enter the name of your bot and select the Telegram platform.
3. Get a token
4. Configure the bot settings
Provide basic information about your bot, including its description and purpose.
Determine the access rights and capabilities of the bot (optional)
